{"tid":1916732,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"同今時今日仲唔夠口罩用嘅人講","createTime":"2020-03-09T05:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T20:05:33.000Z","uid":308377,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a52926a16f69d5436dc8f882ee1e1c592bf910f1","tid":1916732,"uid":308377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:07:55.000Z","msg":"啱呀，你哋咪繼續屌人炒狗囉<br />\n自己價低唔買<br />\n提你地會升又屌鬼<br />\n依家咪升幾倍囉<br />\n呢個世界做好人無用嫁<br />\n唔怪之得場運動搞禁耐都係咁<br />\n話自己同支那人唔同<br />\n咪又做埋一樣嘅嘢<br />\n有事就道德撚上身<br />\n冇事就話有製作恐荒<br />\n<br />\n到今日呢刻你都會唔夠口罩用全部都係抵死<br />\n足足兩月，依家第三個月<br />\n中肺炎啦，死偽黃港豬<br />\n到時驚死，你班仆街咪死死地氣屌老母照買<br />\n香港會有今日唔怪得政苦<br />\n個個都抵死"},{"pid":"cdf6e61eeb8cb511ac374b0ab932af98fe228e70","tid":1916732,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:39:01.000Z","msg":"香港人要堅持平過60蚊1盒先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中肺炎都唔益炒狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423bd868c35603c2ec98021b3985b7ec261ad4f3","tid":1916732,"uid":8410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"前日出街已經見到好多人唔戴口罩， 好多人覺得確診數字回落"},{"pid":"f986dd4b770dae64a70d4be51d852d47f3bd6194","tid":1916732,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"而家幾多錢一盒？"},{"pid":"9371204e88ebbb103f5627a2a1b35cccfeb0415b","tid":1916732,"uid":272652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"藥房開post?"},{"pid":"474bb4627e795ec3c88de7a3f2871bddc230ddd9","tid":1916732,"uid":266410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f986dd4b770dae64a70d4be51d852d47f3bd6194","tid":1916732,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"而家幾多錢一盒？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"早2日經過深水埗，已經見到180 1盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a7443054d